693
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:06,660
one by one,

694
00:32:08,350 --> 00:32:10,420
and then watch the wet ground

695
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:11,660
as it dried up.

696
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:15,940
Think about it now.

697
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:19,050
Those scenes were so many years ago.

698
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,620
So why do you dance?

699
00:32:25,790 --> 00:32:27,010
Because wearing a skirt is pretty,

700
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:29,180
